{"tid":1966874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★芬蘭科學家製3D模型　證病毒停留在空氣中更久","createTime":"2020-04-10T13:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T08:24:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0f088b8a6c9a452546bb2ecb7324cdf31ba72b","tid":1966874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"科學家們發布一個3D模型，展示新冠病毒在人咳嗽、打噴嚏以及說話時，如個通過空氣中極細小的氣溶膠顆粒運送。<br />\n<br />\n他們說基於這個發現，建議人們在新冠肺炎疫情期間應避免置身人多的室內空間。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員的模型，模擬一個人在一列櫃之間咳嗽，情況有此人站在超級市場內、貨架與貨架之間的走道。<br />\n<br />\n他們發現氣溶膠雲可擴散至咳嗽人士附近以外的地方以及稀釋，但需時達數分鐘。而氣溶膠雲會蔓延到隔鄰的貨架。<br />\n<br />\n阿爾托大學助理沃里寧（Ville Vuorinen）指出，有些受感染的人在咳嗽後走開了，但他們留下攜帶病毒的、極細的氣溶膠顆粒：「這些顆粒最終可能進入附近的人的呼吸道。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/459647/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%8A%AC%E8%98%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E8%A3%BD3d%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E8%AD%89%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%81%9C%E7%95%99%E5%9C%A8%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E4%B8%AD%E6%9B%B4%E4%B9%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F459647%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%258A%25AC%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A3%25BD3d%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%259E%258B-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259B%25B4%25E4%25B9%2585&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6zDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=6774ffa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/459647/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%8A%AC%E8%98%AD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E8%A3%BD3d%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E8%AD%89%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%81%9C%E7%95%99%E5%9C%A8%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E4%B8%AD%E6%9B%B4%E4%B9%85</a>"},{"pid":"7c389f017bd4a1bd3a4a6be3063d2a88e9b3c3ca","tid":1966874,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited